HOUR - Static variable in class clock.CurrentClockText
Show the current hour only for example: 18.
HOUR_MINUTE - Static variable in class clock.CurrentClockText
Show the current hour and minute for example: 18:47.
HOUR_MINUTE_SECOND - Static variable in class clock.CurrentClockText
Show the current hour, minute and second for example: 18:47:16.
HOUR_MINUTE_SECOND_MILLISECOND - Static variable in class clock.CurrentClockText
Show the current hour, minute, second and millisecond for example: 18:47:16.234.
